project: Use WASD or Arrow Keys to Move and S or Down Arrow to duck
Jump on the side of the wall to hang on to it. Don't hold down up arrow when trying to grab the wall. Jump and point in the direction you want to go to let go.
Run and press down arrow or S to slide. If you get stuck press r to restart
Press Shift to activate the ladder and use WASD or Arrow Keys to move.
Press the Spacebar in order to shoot in the direction you are standing
Press Z while standing over the gold to pick it up
Pick up the torch by pressing z and drop it by pressing x. Light the torch stands by pressing z. Light all of the torch stands to open the door.
